data.description: Welcome to your dream home nestled on a serene 2-acre surveyed lot with mature trees, offering the perfect blend of privacy and convenience. This charming 3-bedroom home has over 1700 square feet.  Don't let the street fool you, this home sets well back from Midland Road.  In the heart of the home awaits in the form of a spacious and inviting kitchen. Boasting refaced cabinets, with newer doors, drawers with soft close.  The large kitchen space is perfect for entertaining friends and family, making it the focal point of gatherings and creating lasting memories.  Upstairs has two large bedrooms on both ends.  With a large updated full bath and 3rd bedroom between in-between.    This prime location places you in close proximity to the center of the Tri Cities and just down the street from the Tittabawassee Township Park.  Call your favorite Realtor for a showing today!
